snippet.title: FAVELA WARS Promo Trailer (Official English version)
snippet.description:
http://www.favelawars.com

This official promo video presents the game Favela Wars, the turn based strategy game set in Rio de Janeiro's slums. Live the drug wars from a strategic standpoint!
